<article>
  <h1>Installation</h1>

  <p>You can install "uiloos" in two ways: either via a package manager, or via a CDN.</p>

  <h2>1. Via a package manager</h2>

  <p>You can install "uiloos" via any package manager.</p>

  <h3>Core</h3>

  <p>
    <span class="high">@uiloos/core</span> should always be installed.
    <span class="high">@uiloos/core</span> can be installed via your package manager of choice
  </p>

  {% highlight "bash" %}
npm install @uiloos/core
yarn add @uiloos/core
pnpm add @uiloos/core
  {% endhighlight %}

  <h3>Bindings</h3>

  <p>
    "uiloos" has bindings for various frameworks, you should install 
    the bindings for your framework of choice:
  </p>


  {% highlight "bash" %}
npm install @uiloos/alpine
npm install @uiloos/react
npm install @uiloos/vue
npm install @uiloos/svelte
npm install @uiloos/angular
  {% endhighlight %}

  <h2>2. Via a CDN</h2>

  <p>
    The <span class="high">@uiloos/core</span> and <span class="high">@uiloos/alpine</span> packages
    provide minified builds.
  </p>

  <p>
    You can install "uiloos" by using a CDN such as 
    <a href="https://unpkg.com/browse/@uiloos/core@latest/dist/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline">
      UNPKG
    </a>. When using a CDN make sure that you load each component separately:

{% highlight "html" %}
<!-- Always load the license checker first -->
<script
  src="https://unpkg.com/@uiloos/core@{VERSION}/dist/uiloos-license-checker-{VERSION}.min.js"
  defer
></script>

<!-- Now include what you need from uiloos -->
<script
  src="https://unpkg.com/@uiloos/core@{VERSION}/dist/uiloos-active-list-{VERSION}.min.js" 
  defer>
</script>
<script
  src="https://unpkg.com/@uiloos/core@{VERSION}/dist/uiloos-view-channel-{VERSION}.min.js" 
  defer>
</script>
<script
  src="https://unpkg.com/@uiloos/core@{VERSION}/dist/uiloos-typewriter-{VERSION}.min.js" 
  defer>
</script>

<!-- Only if you are using Alpine.js you should load these  -->
<script
  src="https://unpkg.com/@uiloos/alpine@{VERSION}/dist/uiloos-alpine-active-list-{VERSION}.min" 
  defer>
</script>
<script
  src="https://unpkg.com/@uiloos/alpine@{VERSION}/dist/uiloos-alpine-view-channel-{VERSION}.min" 
  defer>
</script>
<script
  src="https://unpkg.com/@uiloos/alpine@{VERSION}/dist/uiloos-alpine-typewriter-{VERSION}.min" 
  defer>
</script>
<script
  src="https://unpkg.com/@uiloos/alpine@{VERSION}/dist/uiloos-alpine-typewriter-from-sentences-{VERSION}.min" 
  defer>
</script>
{% endhighlight %}
